{
  "stem": "11472.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I knew I had to start to help my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to start watching out for my sister, even though my grandmother and my aunts took care of her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I became my mother's helper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had that little store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to watch they shouldn't steal from her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They shouldn't rob her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the Ukrainian women, the peasants, would come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would come like a bunch, and they would try to, you know-- I became, in 19-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this is-- we're, we're now in the beginning of '45.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In May, the 9th, 1945, the war was over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Polish citizens were allowed to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the pact that Stalin made with Roosevelt and Churchill, that the Polish citizens would be able to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even those from Siberia, they had to leave, all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Also, I forgot to tell you, my Aunt Chana went to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Her husband was in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She went to meet her husband, [NON-ENGLISH], in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We took [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] our possessions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We got on cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went to a town with the name of Bytom to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We went with Polish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While we were on the Ukrainian side, on the Russian side of the border, they were our friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Once we crossed the Russian border and we came on Polish territory, they started to show their colors, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We came to Bytom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In Bytom, they had a Jewish agency already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- Bytom was Germany, but it was part of Poland, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Silesia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Silesia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had already some-- from the Jewish agency, there were people.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
